definitions.definition: A long bench with a high back and arms, often with chest or storage space underneath.
A place made lower than the rest; a wide step or platform lower than some other part. ( Compare a depression . )

main_definition: ( archaic ) A seat of any kind.
secondary_definitions: ( now rare ) A long bench with a high back and arms, often with chest or storage space underneath.
( obsolete ) A place made lower than the rest; a wide step or platform lower than some other part. ( Compare a depression . )
